## Runtime Requirements

### Node Version
- **ALWAYS** use Node v24 to run or build the web app
- Backend can use Node v20+
- Specified in `package.json` engines field

### Package Manager
- Use `npm 10.7.0` (workspaces enabled)
- Never use yarn or pnpm
- Run `npm install` from repo root

